==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Aggressor
<hw>Ag*gres"sor</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>agresseur</ets>.]</ety> <def>The person who first attacks or makes
an aggression; he who begins hostility or a quarrel; an
assailant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The insolence of the <qex>aggressor</qex> is usually proportioned
to the tameness of the sufferer.</q> <rj><qau>Ames.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aggrievance</ent>⟦br⟧
